content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 810.11 - Coordination with the Department of Health

State Regulations

In order to avoid duplication of administrative effort, those
proposed actions which require a review by both the Office and the Department
of Health shall be subject to a single review coordinated by the

Office. Notes
